.TE
.sp 1
.sp
Besides, by using zstyle command, you can change default value:
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
$ zstyle ":zplug:tag" ignore "*\&.plugin\&.zsh"
.fi
.if n \{\
.RE
.\}
.SH "EXAMPLES"
.sp
Ignore oh\-my\-zsh main file:
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
$ zplug "plugins/brew", \e
    from:oh\-my\-zsh, \e
    if:"[[ ${(L)OSTYPE} == *darwin* ]]", \e
    ignore:oh\-my\-zsh\&.sh
.fi
.if n \{\
.RE
.\}
